This is Plughole, a bouncing-ball accelerometer game by Ian Cameron
Smith (headstay); released under GPL.  See "COPYING" for license information.

Includes MTRandom by David Beaumont, released under LGPL.  See
"COPYING-MTRandom" for license information.

Tilt the device to roll your ball around the maze.  Avoid lava traps and make
it to the exit before the clock runs out. 

For full information, please see the project home page:

	http://code.google.com/p/plughole/

This program is distributed in the hope that it will be useful,
but WITHOUT ANY WARRANTY; without even the implied warranty of
